expression: "parse!\n(indoc!\n{\"\n        fn filter([], f) { [] }\n        fn filter([x, ...xs], f) if f(x) { [x, ...filter(xs, f)] }\n        fn filter([x, ...xs], f) { rec filter(xs, f) }\n    \"})"
